# Far-Field Pressure Obstruction

Reusable findings on the nonlocal pressure term that survives localization in the
Navier-Stokes De Giorgi framework.

## Entries

- `exact-surviving-far-field-pairing.md`: full formula for `I_p^far` and the
  dominant `grad phi_k` contribution.
- `constant-harmonic-mode-is-automatically-killed.md`: the divergence pairing
  annihilates constants without extra structure.
- `affine-and-higher-harmonic-modes-survive-as-moments.md`: affine and higher
  harmonic content remains live through moments of `F_k = v_k phi_k^2 e_hat`.
- `bad-coefficient-stays-at-fixed-energy-scale.md`: the operative inherited
  bound uses `C_far ~ ||u||_{L^2}^2 / r_k^3`, not a shrinking `U_k`-dependent
  coefficient.
- `real-progress-requires-a-smaller-effective-coefficient.md`: any genuine gain
  must shrink the coefficient on the full far-field pairing.
- `minimum-threshold-is-positive-margin-net-shrinkage-on-the-same-full-pairing.md`:
  once the full pairing is frozen, the minimum serious threshold is a
  positive-margin net reduction of that same coefficient after later debt is
  repaid.
- `same-scale-exterior-or-harmonic-remainder-is-immediate-failure-on-the-full-pairing.md`:
  same-scale exterior or harmonic freedom is an immediate branch failure unless
  the reconstructed full pairing comes back with a genuinely smaller
  coefficient.
- `generic-harmonic-regularity-fails-the-tao-gate.md`: harmonic-analysis-only
  upgrades do not survive the Tao filter for this branch.
- `algebraic-rewrites-and-local-geometry-fail-the-tao-gate.md`: exact
  `u . grad u` repackagings and local geometry do not act on the live remote
  pressure coefficient.
- `tao-sensitivity-is-only-an-admission-screen-unless-the-full-pairing-coefficient-shrinks.md`:
  averaged-model sensitivity is mandatory, but it only counts if it cashes out
  as coefficient shrinkage on the same full pairing.
- `pressure-tensor-identity-remains-only-a-narrow-testable-possibility.md`:
  the pressure-tensor relation survives only as a moment-cancellation question.
- `harmonic-tail-branch-should-stay-on-the-negative-result-track.md`: the
  branch should not be green-lit beyond one narrow tensor-focused follow-up.
- `step-009-endpoint-gate-is-cleared-on-the-frozen-far-field-ledger.md`:
  the far-field branch now clears Step-009 narrowly, with prior-art and
  packaging screening next and no tensor package admitted yet.
- `prior-art-overlap-collapses-the-live-menu-to-one-pressure-hessian-family-with-no-novelty-clearance.md`:
  the Step-010 overlap screen collapses the remaining menu to one
  pressure-Hessian / strain-defect family attached to `I_p^far`, treats
  harmonic-moment language as only a mechanism subquestion, demotes
  alignment/eigenframe/restricted-Euler labels to comparators or aliases, and
  records that no novelty-cleared survivor exists yet.

